highlights.text: Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “X ÚLTIMA VEZ” is the highest at #36.
“As It Was” by Harry Styles is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #1.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 270 weeks straight.
“Leave The Door Open” by Bruno Mars, Anderson .Paak, and Silk Sonic is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 108 spots at #89.
